{"tid":1738974,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"11月24日  區選角色募集","createTime":"2019-11-19T12:07:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T14:12:09.000Z","uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca3e05266653df566a3577bf2eb64b6e75f1784","tid":1738974,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:07:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>下一場超級大戰 <br />\n11月24日的攻略</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n無論你認不認同區選，希望你能看完! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n準備長期抗爭! 三年五年十年甚至更遠，我們要做既好簡單 : 增加更多據點 ! <br />\n<br />\n目的：將魔物趕出議會為社區大白象工程設關卡 ! 阻止天價17億元行人天橋和智能燈再出現 ! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🚨請全港真市民聽住：<br />\n<br />\n11月24日</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 全民孝順日：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n一早起床，全家總動員。<br />\n7：30前就要關心住安老院捨的家人，一早要幫他們拿回屬於他們身份證，陪伴他們一整天。甚至可以的話，簡述最近發生既大事，一起飲茶食早餐，然後一起去投票！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 超合作口投市民：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n記得找調查員，一律口投建制派。人地會問你上屆立法會、區議會投邊個，記得早點找資料。口投完，附近hea一陣繼續入票站，出返來，繼續口投。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 公眾助選員和監票員：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n請預留時間，全日要stand by，一系助選，一系監察票站，做得就做。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>[black]<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 超級和理非票站民間保安員：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>[/black]</strong><br />\n<br />\n投完就一路守著票站，預防一切可能性的破壞，包括喬裝破壞票站，有人換票箱，睇住電箱預防突然大停電。無論對家做什麼，切記一定要和理非。有人破壞，即系鬼，即刻制服。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>天佑我城，香港團結！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e7cdaec609421a58a972a237ea15d714cc61fe03","tid":1738974,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:08:26.000Z","msg":"甴維尼 壹"},{"pid":"0949ada7e70773b8f8c26713dff0f763cf573042","tid":1738974,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:08:40.000Z","msg":"甴維尼 貳"},{"pid":"6fe036f0931b3eb61777894946ecef6bf3d67eba","tid":1738974,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:08:50.000Z","msg":"甴維尼 叄"},{"pid":"c5d9c3743c99ee4fbbd928f1d06809ece4ad3766","tid":1738974,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:09:02.000Z","msg":"甴維尼 肆"},{"pid":"e4f4e94c29ed39ed48912fb744ba606aff707a1f","tid":1738974,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:09:14.000Z","msg":"甴維尼 伍"},{"pid":"1f590ecb81db49a5868aaa624d3c716a0cca9401","tid":1738974,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:09:25.000Z","msg":"甴維尼 陸"},{"pid":"3445227fc0be9d9ca7a6336ade3edba72b8520d2","tid":1738974,"uid":302758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:09:34.000Z","msg":"無力幫推"},{"pid":"1e51609b7645f907e69eadf5f90d74bbc3b22550","tid":1738974,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:09:50.000Z","msg":"甴維尼 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">柒</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9856f87b2e78c0a3d39d41ed890d83b793abf54b","tid":1738974,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:10:04.000Z","msg":"甴維尼 捌"},{"pid":"16c8fbc4058b2300b84fe1c88bbf7fa97845b6ac","tid":1738974,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:10:18.000Z","msg":"甴維尼 玖"},{"pid":"ea5ff914e27fd4288224741385bc735be3731888","tid":1738974,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dis